                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#143r"/> Excerpt from <title type="complete" ref="LIT3851Hassab"/>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a02">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#142v"/>: Days in the year on which heaven is open to receive prayers, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ርኅወ፡ ሰማይ፡</foreign>
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ታእምር፡ ርኅወ፡ ሰማይ፡ ዘይጼልዩ፡ ቦቱ፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘላእለ፡ ማያት፡ ወእምዝ፡ ይጠመቁ፡ በውእቱ፡ ማይ፡ ወይሰትዩ፡ እምኔሁ፡ ለትፈውሶ፡ ወለረድኤት፡ ወይከውን፡ ዝንቱ፡ አመ፡ ፳ ለጥቅምት፡ . . .</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e01">
                    <desc>
                    <locus target="#ir(ecto) #iv(erso) #iir(ecto) #iiv(erso) #iiir(ecto) #iiiv(erso) #142r #143v"/> blank and pen trials
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e02">
                    <desc>
                    Identified in the insurance hand list as Psalter 4
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e03">
                    <desc>
                      Navigation system:
                      blue string is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#20 #29 #48 #58 #93 #101 #119 #126"/>; white string is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#41"/>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e04">
                    <desc>
                    Numbered quires: quires 2–11
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e05">
                    <desc>
                    Psalm 118 contains the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e06">
                    <desc>
                    Scribal intervention:
                    words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#2r #6r #7v #11v #13r"/> #etc.);
                    and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#33r #46v #80v #89v"/>);
                    and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#60r"/>, line 2), and in another case where the symbol (+) is used (<locus target="#125v"/>, line 18);
                    text has been removed (<locus target="#5v #8r #28v #59v #131r"/>, etc.)
                  </desc>
                    </item>
